{"tid":2374800,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（時事台之友-Lunch哥）庭上舉五一手勢稱「拉筋」　官斥「咩事啊你？」","createTime":"2021-01-21T13:28:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T13:46:03.000Z","uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1435f8f836d8ebaa38ead09818cc087727eb3046","tid":2374800,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T13:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n被稱「Lunch哥」的學生李國永被指在職業訓練局15歲女生陳彥霖的死因研訊首日，與一名65歲女子在庭外滋擾陳彥霖母親等人，早前被控非法集結罪，案件今（21日）於西九龍裁判法院再提堂。「Lunch哥」在散庭之際舉起「五一」手勢，主任裁判官羅德泉斥「咩事啊你？向公眾席舉手勢係咩意思？」辯方律師向法庭致歉，羅官表明「法庭唔係表達事項的地方，唔好將依啲嘢帶入法庭」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20210121/s00001/1611206356682/「lunch哥」涉滋擾陳彥霖母控非法集結-庭上舉五一手勢稱「拉筋」-官斥「咩事啊你-」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20210121%2Fs00001%2F1611206356682%2F%E3%80%8Clunch%E5%93%A5%E3%80%8D%E6%B6%89%E6%BB%8B%E6%93%BE%E9%99%B3%E5%BD%A5%E9%9C%96%E6%AF%8D%E6%8E%A7%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90-%E5%BA%AD%E4%B8%8A%E8%88%89%E4%BA%94%E4%B8%80%E6%89%8B%E5%8B%A2%E7%A8%B1%E3%80%8C%E6%8B%89%E7%AD%8B%E3%80%8D-%E5%AE%98%E6%96%A5%E3%80%8C%E5%92%A9%E4%BA%8B%E5%95%8A%E4%BD%A0-%E3%80%8D&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcGrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=7c2adb45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20210121%2Fs00001%2F1611206356682%2F%E3%80%8Clunch%E5%93%A5%E3%80%8D%E6%B6%89%E6%BB%8B%E6%93%BE%E9%99%B3%E5%BD%A5%E9%9C%96%E6%AF%8D%E6%8E%A7%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90-%E5%BA%AD%E4%B8%8A%E8%88%89%E4%BA%94%E4%B8%80%E6%89%8B%E5%8B%A2%E7%A8%B1%E3%80%8C%E6%8B%89%E7%AD%8B%E3%80%8D-%E5%AE%98%E6%96%A5%E3%80%8C%E5%92%A9%E4%BA%8B%E5%95%8A%E4%BD%A0-%E3%80%8D&h=81eb452f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20210121/s00001/1611206356682/「lunch哥」涉滋擾陳彥霖母控非法集結-庭上舉五一手勢稱「拉筋」-官斥「咩事啊你-」</a>"},{"pid":"75e824ecf5c35c793776b5a429f795f430502d0e","tid":2374800,"uid":2